is because of me.

202
00:14:03,580 --> 00:14:05,780
记住了
Remember that.

203
00:14:43,950 --> 00:14:47,460
殿下驾临  倍感荣幸
Your Highness. I'm honoured.

204
00:14:48,710 --> 00:14:50,220
