Thank you.

205
00:15:15,140 --> 00:15:17,480
你做了些改动啊
You have made changes.

206
00:15:17,750 --> 00:15:21,300
是的  这里需要女人的打理
Yes, it needed a woman's touch.

207
00:15:21,450 --> 00:15:25,150
