Come on. I'm sure you'd like to relax before dinner.

208
00:15:25,400 --> 00:15:30,020
薇薇安会照顾你  带你去你的寝宫
Vivian will look after you and show you to your chambers.

209
00:15:32,150 --> 00:15:33,370
梅林
Merlin,

210
00:15:33,970 --> 00:15:35,440
你随我来
you're with me.

211
00:15:38,380 --> 00:15:40,850
