No.

278
00:19:45,060 --> 00:19:46,940
没事
No, it's fine.

279
00:19:47,250 --> 00:19:50,270
如果你不介意的话  我现在要睡了
Now, if you don't mind, i'd quite like to pass out.

280
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:51,850
