Your Highness.

283
00:19:56,340 --> 00:19:57,750
叫我亚瑟就行了
Just Arthur.

284
00:19:57,910 --> 00:19:59,190
好吧
Yes.

285
00:19:59,900 --> 00:20:01,360
就叫你亚瑟
Just Arthur.

286
00:20:15,330 --> 00:20:17,260
你那无畏的战士
So your fearless warrior

287
00:20:17,260 --> 00:20:19,480
