你的国王需要你的服务
Your king requires your service.

293
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:28,910
我不认识什么国王
I don't recognize any king.

294
00:21:28,910 --> 00:21:30,430
好吧  但他认识你
Well, he recognizes you.

295
00:21:31,270 --> 00:21:32,960
