And he demands your loyalty.

296
00:21:33,120 --> 00:21:34,390
是你
You.

297
00:21:35,850 --> 00:21:37,180
我告诉过你了
I've told you before,

298
00:21:37,180 --> 00:21:38,360
我没兴趣效忠尤瑟
I'm not interested in serving Uther.

299
00:21:38,500 --> 00:21:40,260
你说过他很棒
I thought you said he was good.

300
00:21:40,260 --> 00:21:41,360
好像也不咋样
He's not that good.

301
00:21:42,290 --> 00:21:44,110
卡米洛特有很多他这样的男人
Camelot's got plenty of men as good as him.

302
00:21:44,250 --> 00:21:45,110
谁是卡米洛特
Who's Camelot?

303
00:21:45,110 --> 00:21:46,400
那不是一个人  是个地方
It's not a who; it's a place.

304
00:21:46,540 --> 00:21:48,550
那里是我的兄弟  亚瑟王  统治的国家
From where my brother, King Arthur, rules the country.

305
00:21:48,660 --> 00:21:50,770
不是我瞧不起他  他不是国王
Not my bit, he doesn't.

306
00:21:50,770 --> 00:21:51,640
你对他没有任何了解
You don't know anything about him.

307
00:21:51,780 --> 00:21:54,170
